  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc0 18 \u0daf\u0dcf - 19 \u0daf\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "First petrol ship between 18th - 19th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Power and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said that the first ship carrying petrol to Sri Lanka is scheduled to arrive between the 18th and 19th.",
        "He also said that a ship carrying diesel arrived this morning and another ship carrying diesel is scheduled to arrive tonight."
      ],
